#
# Wacom configuration
#

config EPEN_WACOM_WEZ01
	tristate "Wacom penabled i2c touchscreen"
	depends on I2C
	help
	  Say Y here if you have an Wacom penabled i2c touchscreen
	  connected to your system.

	  If unsure, say N.

	  To compile this driver as a module, choose M here: the
	  module will be called wacom.

config EPEN_WACOM_W9020
	bool "Wacom W9020 penabled i2c touchscreen"
	depends on EPEN_WACOM_WEZ01
	help
	  Say Y here if you are using the W9020 digitizer instead of WEZ01.